quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  54,23,AmaThamûd asala isilumkiso
  54,24,"Athi:“Ingabangumntuomnyephakathikwethuesizakulandela yena? Inene singaba sekulahlekeni nasempambanweni"
  54,25,Ingaba umyalezo uthunyelwe kuye phakathi kwethu? Hayi khona lixoki elingenazintloni (lo)!”
  54,26,"Baza\tkumazi\tngomso\tukuba\tngubani\tna\tolixoki elingenazintloni"
  54,27,"Inene Thina Sithumele ithokazi lenkamela ukuba libe luvavanyo kubo, bajonge ke ube nomonde"
  54,28,"Ubaxelele kananjalo okokuba amanzi baza kwahlulelana ngawo, (Nenkamela), ngenye (imini) kuza kusela bona (ize ibe yinkamela ngenye imini)"
  54,29,"Kodwa bona babiza ugxa wabo2, waba nesibindi wayinqumla imisipha"
  54,30,Saba njani ke (ukuba buhlungu) iSohlwayo saM nesilumkiso
  54,31,Inene Thina Sathoba isiqhushumbisi phezu kwabo baba ngathi ziintsasa ezomileyo ezizizijungqu zesibaya sezilwanyana
  54,32,"Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke, ukhona na phofu oza kukhumbula"
  54,33,Abantu bakwaLût basala isilumkiso
  54,34,"Inene, Thina Sathumela isiphango samatye phezu kwabo ngaphandle kosapho lukaLût, lona Salusindisa phambi koms’obomvu"
  54,35,NgoBabalo oluvela kuThi. Simvuza kanjalo ke onombulelo
  54,36,"Ke kaloku yena wayesele ebalumkisile (kwantlandlolo) ngohlaselo lweThu, kodwa bona basiphikisa isilumkiso"
  54,37,"Kananjalo bafuna ukuxhwila iindwendwe zakhe, Kodwa Sabamfamekisela amehlo abo (SiSithi): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso ke.”"
  54,38,Ke kaloku ekuseni bafikelwa sisohlwayo esibuhlungu
  54,39,"(Kwathiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo saM nesilumkiso ke.”"
  54,40,Kananjalo Siyenze i’Kur’ân yalula ukuba ikhumbuleke kodwa ukhona na phofu oza kukhumbula